Nigeria’s leading beverage brand, Coca-Cola has rolled out a N400 million promotional offer for all football lovers and consumers alike tagged:  the Under-The-Crown promo to reward EPL fans. The promo would give out instant cash prizes in what is possibly the biggest industry reward programmed for football fans in Nigeria today.  It kicked off in March 2020, and would  reward 10 lucky consumers with an all-expense paid trip to watch a live EPL game and also visit iconic locations in the United Kingdom. The promo would end on May 31, 2020. To participate, consumers are required to simply purchase and enjoy a promotional bottle of Coke Classic or Coke Zero, look under the crown for the unique code. According to the marketing manager, Coca-Cola Nigeria, Ltd Ajiborode Abiodun, the promotion serves as a reward for the brand’s teeming consumers and lovers of the English premier league in Nigeria. He reinforced that the brand’s commitment would satisfy consumers with great tasting Coca-Cola experience whilst rewarding them for their loyalty. “For us, it is all about refreshing our world and making a difference in the life of our consumers,” he concluded.